'''聖加西彌祿教堂'''（{{lang-pl|Warszawski kościół Sakramentek pod wezwaniem św. Kazimierza}}）是[[波蘭|波蘭]]首都[[華沙|華沙]]的一座[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]的[[教堂|教堂]]，位於[[華沙新城區|華沙新城區]]。教堂原本是一座宮殿，在1688年被改建為教堂。在[[華沙起義|華沙起義]]期間，教堂曾被用作醫院，因此遭到了德軍的猛烈轟炸<ref name="sakramentki">{{cite web |author =  |url = http://www.sakramentki.opoka.org.pl/hist_kosc.htm |title = Historia kościoła św. Kazimierza |work = www.sakramentki.opoka.org.pl |publisher =  |pages =  |page =  |date =  |accessdate = 2008-07-09 |language = pl |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20091120185738/http://www.sakramentki.opoka.org.pl/hist_kosc.htm |archive-date = 2009-11-20 |dead-url = yes }}</ref><ref name="sztuka">{{cite web |author = Paweł Giergoń |url = http://www.sztuka.net.pl/palio/html.run?_Instance=www.sztuka.net.pl&_PageID=445&newsId=284&callingPageId=487&_CheckSum=785059985 sztuka.net |title = Kościół św. Kazimierza |work = www.sztuka.net.pl |publisher =  |pages =  |page =  |date =  |accessdate = 2008-07-09 |language = pl |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070927222811/http://www.sztuka.net.pl/palio/html.run?_Instance=www.sztuka.net.pl&_PageID=445&newsId=284&callingPageId=487&_CheckSum=785059985 |archivedate = 2007-09-27 }}</ref>。教堂在1947年至1953年期間得到重建<ref>{{cite web|author =|url =http://www.varsovia.pl/varsovia/index.php-frame=main&mapa=0&item=3507&top=23.htm|title =Zespół kościelno-klasztorny Sakramentek na Rynku Nowego Miasta|work =www.varsovia.pl|publisher =|pages =|page =|date =|accessdate =2008-07-09|language =pl|deadurl =yes|archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20080613214004/http://www.varsovia.pl/varsovia/index.php-frame%3Dmain%26mapa%3D0%26item%3D3507%26top%3D23.htm|archivedate =2008-06-13}}</ref>。

